---
import Page from '../../components/Page.astro';
import Syncer from './svelte/Syncer.svelte';
---

<Page title="Cloud Sync" columns="1">
    <section class="intro">
        <p>
            Back up or restore your DSPACE saves using a private GitHub Gist. Your token and gist ID
            are stored only in your browser and never sent to DSPACE servers.
        </p>
        <ol>
            <li>
                Create a GitHub personal access token and paste it below (choose one):
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Classic PAT with the <strong>gist</strong> permission (preselected):
                        <a
                            href="https://github.com/settings/tokens/new?scopes=gist&description=DSPACE%20Cloud%20Sync"
                        >
                            https://github.com/settings/tokens/new?scopes=gist&description=DSPACE%20Cloud%20Sync
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Fine-grained PAT:
                        <a href="https://github.com/settings/personal-access-tokens/new">
                            https://github.com/settings/personal-access-tokens/new
                        </a>
                        — grant <strong>Gists: Read and write</strong> (or equivalent), ensure it can access your
                        gists, and treat this token like a password.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
                Enter a Gist ID from the end of a
                <a href="https://gist.github.com/">GitHub Gist URL</a>
                to restore data, or leave it blank and we will create one when you upload.
            </li>
            <li>Use the same token and Gist ID on any device to sync your save data.</li>
        </ol>
    </section>
    <div class="vertical">
        <Syncer client:load />
    </div>
</Page>

<style>
    .vertical {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        width: 100%;
    }

    .intro {
        display: grid;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        margin: 0 auto 1rem;
        width: min(720px, 100%);
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
        border-radius: 0.75rem;
        line-height: 1.4;
    }

    ol {
        margin: 0;
        padding-left: 1.25rem;
        display: grid;
        gap: 0.35rem;
    }

    ul {
        margin: 0.35rem 0;
        padding-left: 1.25rem;
        display: grid;
        gap: 0.25rem;
    }

    a {
        color: #b2f5bf;
    }
</style>
